# MPT Warrior - Mindset Plan Trader Hub

Environment variables setup untuk MPT Warrior

## Required Environment Variables

### Google Gemini AI
NEXT_PUBLIC_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

### Azure Cosmos DB (Optional - untuk production)
NEXT_PUBLIC_COSMOS_CONNECTION_STRING=your_cosmos_connection_string
NEXT_PUBLIC_COSMOS_ENDPOINT=your_cosmos_endpoint
NEXT_PUBLIC_COSMOS_KEY=your_cosmos_key

### Economic Calendar API
NEXT_PUBLIC_ECONOMIC_CALENDAR_API=https://api.example.com/calendar

### Other Services
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=MPT Warrior
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_VERSION=1.0.0

## Development Setup

Untuk development lokal, gunakan nilai default atau setup Cosmos DB emulator:
1. Download Azure Cosmos DB Emulator
2. Jalankan: cosmosdb-emulator
3. Default endpoint: https://localhost:8081/
4. Default key: C2y6yDjf5/R+ob0N8A7Cgv30VRDJIWEHLM+4QkCqFY=

## Production Setup

Untuk production:
1. Create Azure Cosmos DB account
2. Setup Google Gemini API
3. Configure security keys di environment
4. Enable backup dan disaster recovery
